{"tha-ap475:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap475:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap475:0.3":"Ukkasatikattheraapadana ","tha-ap475:1.1":"“Kosiyo nama bhagava, ","tha-ap475:1.2":"cittakute vasi tada; ","tha-ap475:1.3":"Jhayi jhanarato buddho, ","tha-ap475:1.4":"vivekabhirato muni. ","tha-ap475:2.1":"Ajjhogahetva himavantam, ","tha-ap475:2.2":"Nariganapurakkhato; ","tha-ap475:2.3":"Addasam kosiyam buddham, ","tha-ap475:2.4":"Punnamayeva candimam. ","tha-ap475:3.1":"Ukkasate gahetvana, ","tha-ap475:3.2":"parivaresaham tada; ","tha-ap475:3.3":"Sattarattindivam thatva, ","tha-ap475:3.4":"atthamena agacchaham. ","tha-ap475:4.1":"Vutthitam kosiyam buddham, ","tha-ap475:4.2":"sayambhum aparajitam; ","tha-ap475:4.3":"Pasannacitto vanditva, ","tha-ap475:4.4":"ekam bhikkham adasaham. ","tha-ap475:5.1":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap475:5.2":"lokajettha narasabha; ","tha-ap475:5.3":"Uppajjim tusite kaye, ","tha-ap475:5.4":"ekabhikkhayidam phalam. ","tha-ap475:6.1":"Divasanceva rattinca, ","tha-ap475:6.2":"aloko hoti me sada; ","tha-ap475:6.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap475:6.4":"obhasena pharamaham. ","tha-ap475:7.1":"Pancapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap475:7.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap475:7.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap475:7.4":"jambumandassa issaro. ","tha-ap475:8.1":"Tada me nagaram asi, ","tha-ap475:8.2":"iddham phitam sunimmitam; ","tha-ap475:8.3":"Timsayojanamayamam, ","tha-ap475:8.4":"vittharena ca visati. ","tha-ap475:9.1":"Sobhanam nama nagaram, ","tha-ap475:9.2":"vissakammena mapitam; ","tha-ap475:9.3":"Dasasaddavivittam tam, ","tha-ap475:9.4":"sammatalasamahitam. ","tha-ap475:10.1":"Na tamhi nagare atthi, ","tha-ap475:10.2":"vallikatthanca mattika; ","tha-ap475:10.3":"Sabbasonnamayamyeva, ","tha-ap475:10.4":"jotate niccakalikam. ","tha-ap475:11.1":"Catupakaraparikkhittam, ","tha-ap475:11.2":"tayo asum manimaya; ","tha-ap475:11.3":"Vemajjhe talapanti ca, ","tha-ap475:11.4":"vissakammena mapita. ","tha-ap475:12.1":"Dasasahassapokkharanno, ","tha-ap475:12.2":"padumuppalachadita; ","tha-ap475:12.3":"Pundarikehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap475:12.4":"nanagandhasamirita. ","tha-ap475:13.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap475:13.2":"yam ukkam dharayim aham; ","tha-ap475:13.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap475:13.4":"ukkadharassidam phalam. ","tha-ap475:14.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap475:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap475:14.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap475:15.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap475:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap475:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap475:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap475:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap475:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap475:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ukkasatiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap475:18.1":"Ukkasatikattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}